content.rendered: This log book is a convenient way to stay organized and keep track of important details while working with your clients, as well as look and feel professional. This log book will help you to keep track of every session. Tracking every session gives you a detail view of client progress, feedback, goals, limiting beliefs, issues, accountability and follow up plan. There are around 76 coaching sessions to record notes and it also includes a convenient log to keep track of page numbers.
